1. *Sladak* voćni sok je omiljena piće deteta. (The sweet fruit juice is a child's favorite drink.)
2. Ona voli da je njen dečko *sladak*. (She likes her boyfriend to be sweet.)
3. Njegov je osmeh *sladak*. (His smile is sweet.)
4. *Sladko* je bilo slušati muziku. (It was sweet to listen to the music.)
5. On je obožavao *sladak* ukus bombona. (He loved the sweet taste of the candy.)
6. Ona je često donosila *slatke* reči. (She often brought sweet words.)